Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,B2,MUSIC,0000,0000,0000,,(Nagauta Matsu no Midori)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.27,0:01:36.45,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,A New Year’s Special Issue?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.04,0:01:38.15,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.15,0:01:39.52,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,“The Soul Reapers overcoming
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.52,0:01:41.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,their Squads’ differences \Nto welcome the New Year!”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.27,0:01:45.37,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,That’s the theme we’ll be going \Nfor in our next Seireitei Bulletin!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.66,0:01:48.46,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.87,0:01:53.20,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll hold a non-competitive, \Nyet unique Soul Reaper event!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.48,0:01:56.26,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,And I decided to put you in charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.53,0:01:58.65,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.65,0:02:00.13,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,If you complete it successfully,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.13,0:02:04.32,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll give you a huge byline \Nas planner and editor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.32,0:02:05.60,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.13,0:02:06.98,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,It’s set, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:09.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do a good job, Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.24,0:02:10.98,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:15.53,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,I never said a word about accepting...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.44,0:02:20.99,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,He is so bossy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:22.35,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.35,0:02:24.36,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,I’m definitely turning it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.36,0:02:25.44,B2,HINAMORI,0000,0000,0000,,Turn down what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.78,0:02:30.62,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hinamori?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.62,0:02:31.75,B2,HINAMORI,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:33.45,B2,HINAMORI,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you act so surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.45,0:02:35.42,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it’s nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.79,0:02:38.38,B2,HINAMORI,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you turning down?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:39.48,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:41.34,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, it’s...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.60,0:02:42.48,B2,HINAMORI,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.48,0:02:44.32,B2,HINAMORI,0000,0000,0000,,Is it that serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.32,0:02:45.85,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,No, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.68,0:02:48.94,B2,HINAMORI,0000,0000,0000,,But that sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.94,0:02:50.53,B2,HINAMORI,0000,0000,0000,,Why’re you turning it down?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.53,0:02:51.06,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.06,0:02:52.97,B2,HINAMORI,0000,0000,0000,,Having the Squads overcome their
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.97,0:02:54.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,differences to get along \Nis a wonderful thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.87,0:02:56.07,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:59.37,B2,HINAMORI,0000,0000,0000,,Hisagi is entrusting you with this important
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.37,0:03:01.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,task because he trusts you, Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.96,0:03:03.78,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,No...I don’t think that’s why he...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.36,0:03:06.29,B2,HINAMORI,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:09.67,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.67,0:03:10.66,B2,HINAMORI,0000,0000,0000,,I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.66,0:03:12.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:14.96,B2,HINAMORI,0000,0000,0000,,Be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:17.21,B2,HINAMORI,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I’ll be looking \Nforward to your article!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:25.20,B2,KIRA (SOFTLY),0000,0000,0000,,All right…I’ll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.70,0:03:31.27,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,So today, you’ll all be flying kites.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:32.73,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:34.73,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, ready…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.15,0:03:49.12,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,This is a lovely New Year’s sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:52.93,B2,KIRA (M),0000,0000,0000,,Hinamori said she’d be coming later…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.93,0:03:55.33,B2,KIRA (M),0000,0000,0000,,I hope I can make this all \Nexciting before she arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:56.47,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Captain…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.47,0:03:58.50,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,The others’ kites are flying high, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.93,0:04:01.51,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Our kite isn’t doing as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:04.95,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,That’s because you made \Nours look like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.35,0:04:08.47,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why I told you to \Ndo a more ordinary design!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.82,0:04:11.77,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.61,0:04:13.81,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Whose kite is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.15,0:04:19.48,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,What’re you doing, Hisagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.48,0:04:20.67,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Can’t you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.67,0:04:21.44,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,What, is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:24.77,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Uh…we’re the hosts here…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.21,0:04:27.54,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,The purpose of this event is to \Nhave all Squads get along, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.54,0:04:28.91,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,So what’s the issue?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.11,0:04:30.83,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,All right…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:33.43,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Please help make sure everyone has a
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.43,0:04:35.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,good time flying their kites, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.28,0:04:37.02,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:37.84,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.16,0:04:40.50,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,It’s really getting up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.56,0:04:42.46,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.67,0:04:48.39,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Hisagi, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:49.90,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.90,0:04:51.27,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll untangle it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:56.60,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Our string snapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:04:59.43,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,You did that on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.43,0:05:00.68,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t be silly…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.68,0:05:02.87,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe your string was weak?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.87,0:05:04.40,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:07.51,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Squad 11’s weak?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.51,0:05:09.47,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you’re trying to say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.47,0:05:11.47,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, please calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.47,0:05:14.19,B2,YUMICHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,He’s insulted Squad 11’s pride—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.19,0:05:16.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t stand for it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:18.58,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a kite!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.77,0:05:20.12,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Hisagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.12,0:05:23.23,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s see whose kite—yours \Nor mine—flies higher!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:25.30,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,You’re on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.74,0:05:27.60,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.60,0:05:29.73,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let’s do this, Yumichika!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.73,0:05:30.56,B2,YUMICHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.29,0:05:33.06,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Now hold on, both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.48,0:05:34.67,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Hisagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.67,0:05:37.31,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Why’d you have to start an \Nargument from your side?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.31,0:05:38.20,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.20,0:05:41.05,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,It’s theatrics to kick things \Nup a notch. Theatrics!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:42.48,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,There, you see!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:43.93,B2,KIYONE,0000,0000,0000,,Kotsubaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.93,0:05:46.29,B2,KIYONE,0000,0000,0000,,Our Captain will always \Nbe number one, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.29,0:05:48.14,B2,SENTARO,0000,0000,0000,,You bet! Now leave this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.14,0:05:48.86,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.49,0:05:52.87,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a hassle, but since \NCaptain Soi Fon might scold me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.87,0:05:54.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’d better take first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:55.05,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.73,0:05:58.96,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,See? I’ve really kicked \Nthings up, haven’t I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.23,0:06:01.00,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,This can’t be happening…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:01.96,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:02.96,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:05.80,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll give it my best, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:07.83,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.83,0:06:09.47,B2,SHUNSUI,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you’re having a hard time…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.45,0:06:11.97,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Kyoraku…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:14.81,B2,SHUNSUI,0000,0000,0000,,We’re enjoying ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:17.98,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,The two of you…aren’t competing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:21.15,B2,NANAO,0000,0000,0000,,We’re different from those barbarians.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:23.34,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,I’m relieved to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:26.66,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Look, look, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.66,0:06:28.25,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Collision coming! Collision coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.25,0:06:28.75,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.75,0:06:30.61,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,What’re doing to our kite?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:35.26,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, I’ll go after the \Neasy-to-knock-down women’s kite!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.07,0:06:37.04,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Omaeda!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:38.87,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,That’s a cheap shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:40.15,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:42.46,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,It’s you women’s fault for being weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.76,0:06:45.44,B2,NANAO,0000,0000,0000,,Hado Number 31! Shakkaho!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.27,0:06:52.55,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,My kite!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.66,0:06:57.51,B2,NANAO,0000,0000,0000,,Women are weak, and easy \Nto knockdown, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.51,0:06:58.68,B2,NANAO,0000,0000,0000,,I will not tolerate…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.12,0:07:00.69,B2,NANAO,0000,0000,0000,,such insults!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.41,0:07:03.69,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go! Do it! Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:05.52,B2,NANAO,0000,0000,0000,,Shakkaho!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.65,0:07:11.86,B2,KIYONE,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Success!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:14.47,B2,SENTARO,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t underestimate Squad 13!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.47,0:07:15.71,B2,SENTARO,0000,0000,0000,,I figured this might happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.71,0:07:18.79,B2,SENTARO,0000,0000,0000,,so I put together a kite using \Nnew materials made in America!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:20.29,B2,KIYONE,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, Kotsubaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.51,0:07:23.18,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.18,0:07:26.10,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,What sort of situation would prompt \Nyou to make a kite like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:28.76,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,What’s that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.14,0:07:34.89,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! Oh yeah! Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.39,0:07:39.68,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,This is our Squad 11 captain’s kite!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.95,0:07:42.98,B2,SHUNSUI,0000,0000,0000,,Things are becoming quite heated…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:44.61,B2,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,No you don’t, Madarame!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:47.61,B2,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,Your kite is no match for mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:52.78,B2,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,You can’t beat our “True \NLady Yoruichi” kite!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:55.32,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Nooooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.42,0:08:00.54,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,It’s no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:02.52,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,This is out of my control…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.27,0:08:06.75,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,That voice…Hinamori?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.07,0:08:08.93,B2,HINAMORI,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.93,0:08:10.76,B2,HINAMORI,0000,0000,0000,,What’s going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:13.22,B2,HINAMORI,0000,0000,0000,,Get me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.44,0:08:14.59,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Hinamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:16.25,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,What is she doing up there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.25,0:08:17.51,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to explain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.13,0:08:20.39,B2,HISAGI (N),0000,0000,0000,,Hinamori, who arrived late to the grounds,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:22.80,B2,HISAGI (N),0000,0000,0000,,became a victim of the kite battle
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.80,0:08:25.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,between the Punishment Force and Squad 11…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:27.63,B2,HISAGI (N),0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.63,0:08:30.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the rope she grabbed was \Npulled skyward by the kite
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:33.31,B2,HISAGI (N),0000,0000,0000,,and that’s how she ended up, up, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.71,0:08:36.77,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be explaining!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.77,0:08:39.97,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,We’ve got to do something \Nand help Hinamori down…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.97,0:08:41.04,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Bankai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:41.75,B2,HISAGI/KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.97,0:08:48.54,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Daiguren Hyorinmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:54.33,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,If that’s the way they want to play,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.33,0:08:56.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,we’ll take down Ikkaku’s kite together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:08:57.67,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Hado Number 58!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.67,0:08:58.74,B2,NANAO/RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Tenran!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.15,0:09:02.96,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll save you, Hinamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.59,0:09:05.85,B2,HINAMORI,0000,0000,0000,,Shiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:09.97,B2,HINAMORI,0000,0000,0000,,Shiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.97,0:09:11.86,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Hinamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:17.91,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Captain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:19.07,B2,NANAO,0000,0000,0000,,Hinamori?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.15,0:09:22.00,B2,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,What was that wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.00,0:09:22.86,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.86,0:09:24.08,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t get distracted!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.23,0:09:25.06,B2,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,What’s that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.06,0:09:26.60,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Go, go, Baldy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.60,0:09:27.74,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Go, go, Meow-Meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.74,0:09:29.36,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best, both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:31.03,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Why…?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.79,0:09:34.83,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Why won’t anyone listen to me…?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.14,0:09:37.00,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your chin up, Izuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.50,0:09:38.80,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Hisagi…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:41.31,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Use this, Izuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:45.23,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Use this to complete your mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:48.23,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is…!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:51.69,B2,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,It’s about time we settle \Nthis once and for all…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.93,0:09:53.13,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.13,0:09:56.15,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll send your kite crashing \Ndown with the next hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.66,0:10:02.41,B2,SOUL REAPERS,0000,0000,0000,,Pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:08.67,B2,SOUL REAPERS,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.22,0:10:13.55,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,I will stop you both myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:16.30,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your head! Wabisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.08,0:10:24.99,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.53,0:10:34.05,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t that…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:35.59,B2,SHUNSUI,0000,0000,0000,,I hope not…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:47.91,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:53.07,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,It’s the start of the New Year—what \Nis the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:10:58.76,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Extra, extra!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:10:58.74,OS,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,SEIREITEI BULLETIN\NGIANT KITE CRASHES INTO SQUAD 1 BARRACKS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:00.43,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Read all about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:01.72,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Extra!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.53,0:11:05.76,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,I’m such a loser…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.36,0:11:15.46,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to make you wait, Renji.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.46,0:11:17.90,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,That’s okay. Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.56,0:11:21.40,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,So, what did you want to \Nsee me about today, Rukia?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.88,0:11:29.83,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Have a drink first!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.34,0:11:33.60,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,This is sake from the World of the Living!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.60,0:11:35.82,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, just one drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.91,0:11:53.96,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Renji!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.13,0:11:56.48,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I asked you here is…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:59.07,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve been asked to perform a dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.30,0:12:04.42,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're having trouble \Ngetting the steps right,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.42,0:12:06.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and that’s why you wanted to talk to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:07.68,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:09.88,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve learned the choreography…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.65,0:12:11.71,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.35,0:12:15.70,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,The Celebration Dance is \Nsomething Hisana once did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:20.65,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Keep that in mind so as not to \Nembarrass the Kuchiki Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:24.51,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve been told that my sister \Ndanced it beautifully…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.48,0:12:28.85,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,I could never match her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.45,0:12:31.21,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.21,0:12:34.72,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,I see, but I’m not sure \NI’m the one to talk to…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.66,0:12:37.61,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.61,0:12:40.20,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, show me this dance of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:42.20,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,You want to see me dance?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:45.26,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t tell whether you’re \Ngood or bad without seeing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.26,0:12:46.82,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose you’re right, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.55,0:12:55.67,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:57.54,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,That was a strange-looking dance…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:12:58.46,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.12,0:13:00.77,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you call it “strange-looking”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.77,0:13:02.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,after coming just to see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.17,0:13:04.20,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Getting angry isn’t going to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.20,0:13:06.20,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Didn’t you think it was \Nstrange-looking yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.78,0:13:09.12,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yes, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.19,0:13:13.63,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Be that as it may, this is one \Nexpensive-looking kimono…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.63,0:13:14.64,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.04,0:13:17.23,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,This piece was painstakingly made
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.23,0:13:20.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,over a long period of \Ntime just for this dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:24.09,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you can get the dance right,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.09,0:13:25.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,there’s no need for you to wear…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.29,0:13:27.07,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.25,0:13:31.36,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia, what’s this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.36,0:13:34.08,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that’s a book on dance for beginners.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:34.71,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:35.50,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.51,0:13:39.57,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia, come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.57,0:13:42.19,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,No, I have to rehearse my dance…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.19,0:13:43.75,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind, let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.75,0:13:45.45,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! Wait, Renji!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:47.89,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t worry! This won’t take long!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.81,0:13:53.85,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,We’ve come with a request!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.13,0:13:56.88,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what’re we doing at Squad 11?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.88,0:13:59.95,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,You’ll see—I want to get stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.76,0:14:07.95,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,Quit slacking, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:09.91,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.50,0:14:12.94,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting has no holidays!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.94,0:14:15.91,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,If you slack, I’ll kill you personally \Nand toss you into the river!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:18.93,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,And what do you guys want?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.37,0:14:21.78,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s join them, Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.78,0:14:23.38,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Why me, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.74,0:14:25.22,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:26.34,B2,KENPACHI,0000,0000,0000,,This’ll be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.25,0:14:32.55,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:35.97,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you planning to do at Squad 10?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:38.52,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind. Just indulge me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:42.52,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,My, what brings the two of you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.05,0:14:45.33,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,The Captain’s not here right now…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.33,0:14:46.98,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,If I do say, Rangiku...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.98,0:14:49.41,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,You look especially ravishing today!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.64,0:14:50.33,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.33,0:14:51.82,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,What’re you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:54.95,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come all this way \Nto sexually harass me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:57.03,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.03,0:15:00.90,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia here wants to learn the \Nsecret of your feminine charms!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.90,0:15:02.25,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Rukia?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:02.94,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.27,0:15:04.54,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:06.92,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Not…really…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.31,0:15:09.53,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.53,0:15:12.01,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,So you’ve finally awakened \Nto your own femininity!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:13.03,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,I said…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.03,0:15:15.10,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Come in, come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:18.29,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:19.37,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,After all the trouble I went through…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.37,0:15:22.10,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t have time for your games!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.27,0:15:28.75,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,How was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.75,0:15:30.16,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.56,0:15:33.91,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t comment when you \Nweren’t even watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:37.57,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,What is that you’re doing today, anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.57,0:15:39.46,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Can’t you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:41.01,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,I’m practicing my New \NYear’s calligraphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.01,0:15:42.88,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Do that at your own place!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:46.29,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Why not give it a try?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.29,0:15:47.02,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:50.73,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Doing calligraphy and calming your mind
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.73,0:15:53.22,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,might help you immerse yourself \Neven further in your dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.55,0:15:55.51,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how it works?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.51,0:15:58.12,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,It can’t hurt to try!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.09,0:16:03.65,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, done!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.83,0:16:04.90,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:06.98,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn’t your mind feel calmer?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:08.09,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,It does…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.52,0:16:09.56,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,By the way…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.56,0:16:10.61,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,What time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.09,0:16:12.87,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,About seven, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.87,0:16:14.11,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Seven?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.11,0:16:15.64,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Is it that late already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:17.36,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.36,0:16:18.51,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t get so flustered!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.51,0:16:19.41,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:22.62,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Because of you, I’ve wasted more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:24.51,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,That’s not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.51,0:16:25.67,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about all I’ve done…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.67,0:16:26.50,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:29.00,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.83,0:16:34.27,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,But…I was trying to…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.27,0:16:35.82,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,I said, go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.82,0:16:37.68,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hear me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.59,0:16:45.06,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:47.46,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Rukia?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.10,0:16:49.12,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.09,0:16:52.31,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,I’m fine…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.58,0:16:59.01,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,The kimono…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.27,0:17:04.00,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.36,0:17:06.87,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,I’m…so sorry, Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.87,0:17:08.49,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,About the kimono, I’ll...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:11.67,B2,RUKIA (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This piece was painstakingly made {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:14.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}over a long period of \Ntime just for this dance!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.11,0:17:19.73,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Get out…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.83,0:17:21.99,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:23.98,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.20,0:17:53.69,B2,OLD MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Master Byakuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.69,0:17:54.60,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.70,0:17:57.01,B2,OLD MAN,0000,0000,0000,,It’s about…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:24.04,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.18,0:18:29.33,B2,KAIEN,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see, Kuchiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.34,0:18:31.79,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Kaien!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:34.92,B2,KAIEN,0000,0000,0000,,I came today to check on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:36.53,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Kaien, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.53,0:18:38.76,B2,KAIEN,0000,0000,0000,,No, don’t say a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:41.30,B2,KAIEN,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, right now you’re…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.99,0:18:44.70,OS,KAIEN,0000,0000,0000,,THE BOY AT THE TEMPLE GATE\N—A CANDLE IN THE WIND
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:43.69,B2,KAIEN,0000,0000,0000,,“The boy at the temple gate—a \Ncandle in the wind”!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.19,0:18:44.72,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.39,0:18:48.32,B2,KAIEN,0000,0000,0000,,You know the proverbs:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.32,0:18:50.12,B2,KAIEN,0000,0000,0000,,“A cornered rat cannot repent.”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.12,0:18:52.65,B2,KAIEN,0000,0000,0000,,“Nothing ventured is \Nworth two in the bush.”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.65,0:18:55.40,B2,KAIEN,0000,0000,0000,,“Out of sight…fall from trees.”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:18:56.44,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Uh…yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.75,0:18:58.40,B2,KAIEN,0000,0000,0000,,But, Kuchiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:19:01.08,B2,KAIEN,0000,0000,0000,,Fear is greater with or without consent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.08,0:19:02.94,B2,KAIEN,0000,0000,0000,,In one ear and a nail in the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.94,0:19:05.39,B2,KAIEN,0000,0000,0000,,Even a worm has a god who will save it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.72,0:19:09.04,B2,KAIEN,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t ever forget that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.51,0:19:11.76,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Please don’t go, Sir Kaien!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.76,0:19:14.24,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:20.46,B2,KAIEN,0000,0000,0000,,When your toes are tired, put \Na chili pepper in your socks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.46,0:19:21.75,B2,KAIEN,0000,0000,0000,,So long!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:24.14,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Kaien!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.92,0:19:30.63,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Kaien!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.89,0:19:39.29,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:43.44,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,What a strange dream…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.11,0:19:51.75,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.26,0:19:57.41,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Hisana wore that kimono
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.41,0:20:00.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,when she performed at the Celebration Dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.67,0:20:03.21,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,You should wear it, as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.21,0:20:05.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,when you dance at this year’s ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.59,0:20:06.60,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.77,0:20:10.32,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,However, what’s important \Nis not the kimono,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.32,0:20:14.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but your attitude towards \Nperforming the dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.40,0:20:16.92,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,You know what I’m talking about…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.37,0:20:20.69,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,There was someone else who said \Nthe same thing before I did…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.94,0:20:25.07,B2,RENJI(i),0000,0000,0000,,Let’s join them, Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.84,0:20:27.66,B2,RENJI(i),0000,0000,0000,,You look especially ravishing today!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:31.58,B2,RENJI(i),0000,0000,0000,,Doing calligraphy and calming your mind…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.08,0:20:34.62,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,That Renji…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.62,0:20:36.87,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,So that’s why he went about \Ndoing all those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.42,0:20:40.51,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia, there’s still time before \Nthe Celebration Ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.41,0:20:44.56,B2,BYAKUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Use that time to practice your dance
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.56,0:20:46.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and not embarrass the Kuchiki Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.18,0:20:49.53,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.09,0:20:53.32,B2,HANATARO,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.32,0:20:55.73,B2,RIKICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, if it isn’t Hanataro…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:20:57.69,B2,HANATARO,0000,0000,0000,,It’s been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.13,0:21:01.77,B2,HANATARO,0000,0000,0000,,I came today to see Lieutenant Abarai…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.77,0:21:04.13,B2,RIKICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Renji?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.13,0:21:06.03,B2,HANATARO,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.03,0:21:07.87,B2,RIKICHI,0000,0000,0000,,No, just that Renji…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:10.41,B2,RIKICHI,0000,0000,0000,,has shut himself up in his \Nroom since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:11.67,B2,HANATARO,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.67,0:21:12.62,B2,HANATARO,0000,0000,0000,,Then…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.64,0:21:15.10,OS,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,TO RENJI ABARAI
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:15.12,B2,HANATARO,0000,0000,0000,,please see that he gets this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.82,0:21:17.34,B2,RIKICHI,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I’ll be sure he gets it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.65,0:21:19.80,B2,HANATARO,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I’ll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.81,0:21:24.86,B2,RIKICHI,0000,0000,0000,,How unusual for Renji to get a letter…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.55,0:21:26.55,B2,RIKICHI,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who it’s from?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.57,0:21:32.33,OS,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,RUKIA KUCHIKI
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.18,0:21:31.32,B2,RUKIA (M),0000,0000,0000,,Dear Renji,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.12,0:21:34.26,B2,RUKIA (M),0000,0000,0000,,This coming January 10th,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.64,0:21:37.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be performing the Celebration Dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.01,0:21:40.52,B2,RUKIA (M),0000,0000,0000,,I’d really like you to come and see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.09,0:21:47.10,B2,RUKIA (M),0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.27,0:23:22.59,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia! Your dance has greatly improved!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.59,0:23:26.03,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! My feet were warm, \Nmaking it easier to perform.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.03,0:23:27.46,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to my advice, no less!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.46,0:23:29.40,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,I kept a chili pepper in my socks!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.40,0:23:31.25,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Kaien was right all along!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.25,0:23:32.47,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,What about my advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.47,0:23:34.57,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much, Sir Kaien!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.01,0:23:36.59,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Another Illustrated Guide for the year!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.13,0:23:38.15,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.15,0:23:39.99,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s have a kite-flying contest!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.39,0:23:41.23,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Keigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.99,0:23:43.19,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,That kite’s humongous!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.38,0:23:44.24,B2,SADO,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.23,0:23:46.74,B2,SADO,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s give it our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.74,0:23:47.61,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.16,0:23:49.05,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.46,0:23:51.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why so glum?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.50,0:23:54.94,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,The Quincy Dance recital is coming up…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.94,0:23:56.29,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not going well…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.50,0:23:58.36,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Q-Quincy dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.36,0:23:59.33,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.63,0:24:00.59,B2,SADO,0000,0000,0000,,You’re on!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.59,0:24:02.29,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,My recital…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.62,0:24:03.18,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.18,0:24:04.62,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,W-What…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.62,0:24:06.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,